            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 2.5",
            "score": 2,
            "is_accepted": true,
            "last_activity_date": 1269865162,
            "creation_date": 1269865162,
            "body": "<p>Yes, you can represent hex ranges in regex:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>boolean matches = string.matches(\"[\\\\x00-\\\\xFF]+\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This will match everything which contains at least one character in the 0x00-0xFF range.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 2537734,
            "question_id": 2537693
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f8db1aa9a5989dda731f9005dbf4a8b8?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
